abstract: >
  Kaplen is a production B2B SaaS platform for converting curriculum
  materials and written content into structured, spoken-word YouTube
  scripts. Built in 32 days at a tooling cost of USD 500 using
  operator-directed AI development with no code written directly.
  Described in the practitioner study "Engineering Without Coding:
  A Practitioner Study of Operator-Driven AI Development" (Azeez, 2026).
